<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung inntha dawtnak ram cu, Mithiang mi hna inn a si, Annih sin kan
 um khawh nakhnga, Vawlei thil kha hlaw cang tuah.

[C1]
   Vawlei ni kha a dongh tikah, A hnu-ah inn nuam ah, A thiangmi an um
   nak khua ah, Van ah kan i din lai.

[V2]
 Zungzal inn nuam chung um hna cu, Inn-chungkhat bantuk an si, Inntha
 chung i um awkah khan, Phun zakip kha an sawm hna.

[C2]
   Vawlei ni kha a dongh tikah, A hnu-ah inn nuam ah, A thiangmi an um
   nak khua ah, Van ah kan i din lai.

[V3]
 A kan Khamhtu thihnak hmun le, Dawtnak bia kha thanter u, Hi
 rian-tuannak a dih hlan ah, A dawtnak bia kha zum tuah.

[C3]
   Vawlei ni kha a dongh tikah, A hnu-ah inn nuam ah, A thiangmi an um
   nak khua ah, Van ah kan i din lai.

[V4]
 Pakhat hnu pakhat in an kal, Inn-chungkhar an tling ti lo,
 Sihmanh-sehlaw dawtmi hna he, Ton-thannak ni a um lai.

[C4]
   Vawlei ni kha a dongh tikah, A hnu-ah inn nuam ah, A thiangmi an um
   nak khua ah, Van ah kan i din lai.</lyrics>
<title>VANCUNG INN THA, DAWTNAK RAM CU CH441</title>
<hymn_number>441</hymn_number>
</song>